quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  29,31,WE LEMMA XHA’ET RUSULUNA ‘IBRAHIME BIL-BUSHRA KALU ‘INNA MUHLIKU ‘EHLI HEDHIHIL-KARJETI ‘INNE ‘EHLEHA KANU DHALIMINE
  29,32,KALE ‘INNE FIHA LUTÆN KALU NEHNU ‘A’LEMU BIMEN FIHA LENUNEXHXHIJENNEHU WE ‘EHLEHU ‘ILLA EMRE’ETEHU KANET MINEL-GABIRIN
  29,33,WE LEMMA ‘EN XHA’ET RUSULUNA LUTÆN SI’E BIHIM WE DAKA BIHIM DHER’ÆN WE KALU LA TEHAF WE LA TEHZEN ‘INNA MUNEXHXHUKE WE ‘EHLEKE ‘ILLA EMRE’ETEKE KANET MINEL-GABIRINE
  29,34,‘INNA MUNZILUNE ‘ALA ‘EHLI HEDHIHIL-KARJETI RIXHZÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I BIMA KANU JEFSUKUNE
  29,35,WE LEKAD TEREKNA MINHA ‘AJETEN BEJJINETEN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  29,36,WE ‘ILA MEDJENE ‘EHAHUM SHU’AJBÆN FEKALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE WE ERXHUL-JEWMEL-’AHIRE WE LA TA’THEW FIL-’ERDI MUFSIDIN
  29,37,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’EHADHET/HUMU ER-REXHFETU FE’ESBEHU FI DARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  29,38,WE ‘ADÆN WE THEMUDE WE KAD TEBEJJENE LEKUM MIN MESAKINIHIM WE ZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘A’MALEHUM FESEDDEHUM ‘ANI ES-SEBILI WE KANU MUSTEBSIRINE
  29,39,WE KARUNE WE FIR’AWNE WE HAMANE WE LEKAD XHA’EHUM MUSA BIL-BEJJINATI FASTEKBERU FIL-’ERDI WE MA KANU SABIKINE
  29,40,FEKULLÆN ‘EHADHNA BIDHENBIHI FEMINHUM MEN ‘ERSELNA ‘ALEJHI HASIBÆN WE MINHUM MEN ‘EHADHET/HU ES-SEJHETU WE MINHUM MEN HASEFNA BIHIL-’ERDE WE MINHUM MEN ‘EGREKNA WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJEDHLIMEHUM WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  29,41,METHELUL-LEDHINE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘EWLIJA’E KEMETHELIL-’ANKEBUTI ETTEHADHET BEJTÆN WE ‘INNE ‘EWHENEL-BUJUTI LEBEJTUL-’ANKEBUTI LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  29,42,‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU MA JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  29,43,WE TILKEL-’EMTHALU NEDRIBUHA LILNNASI WE MA JA’KILUHA ‘ILLAL-’ALIMUNE
  29,44,HALEKAL-LAHU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LILMU’UMININE